Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:38.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まった…\Nあそこに 奇狼丸がいる
Dialogue: 9,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They’ve got us.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:38.08,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s Kiroumaru.
